1. Set environment for casual. i.e CASUAL_BUILD_HOME and CASUAL_HOME

2. Download current version of nginx from http://nginx.org/download/ and build it.

Example:

prompt$ wget http://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.13.5.tar.gz
prompt$ tar xvf nginx-1.13.5.tar.gz
prompt$ cd nginx-1.13.5
prompt$ ./configure --with-cc-opt=-Wno-deprecated --add-module=$CASUAL_BUILD_HOME/middleware/http/source/inbound/plugin
prompt$ make
prompt$ [ ! -d $CASUAL_HOME/http ] && mkdir $CASUAL_HOME/http
prompt$ cp objs/nginx $CASUAL_HOME/http/. && cp $CASUAL_BUILD_HOME/middleware/http/source/inbound/config/* $CASUAL_HOME/http/.

        

